  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Renderer<G>
    Interface for generic renderers.
    Renderers<T>
    Interface which provides the correct parser for a given format.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description

    Class which provides the correct renderer for a given format.

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    RendererNotFoundException

    A generic exception that occurs with renderers.
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    AptRenderer
    Annotation which marks renderers This Annotation can only get used on non-generic non-abstract classes which implement the Renderer interface.
